****************************************
*****DeQuoter v1.0 for Windows 3.1******
*****      From Shadoware         ******
****************************************
Challenging quote decription game that  
features 256 color graphics, digitized  
sound, music, and animations. Over 200  
quotes from Shakespeare to Satchel Paige
will puzzle and entertain you. 
Req: 256 color graphics card. Sound card
is optional.
